</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="474" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="6.[160,1156,853,1155]" box="[160,294,853,878]" pageId="6" pageNumber="474">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,294,853,878]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="474">Description</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[160,1156,853,1155]" pageId="6" pageNumber="474">
<emphasis box="[160,212,887,912]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="474">Male</emphasis>
. Total length: 3.6; prosoma length: 1.8, width: 1.5. Leg I: femur 2.5, patella 0.9, tibia 2.4, metatarsus 2.1, tarsus 0.9. Prosoma dark yellow, eye regions darker, without prominent markings or conspicuous setae. Opisthosoma without spots or markings, folium absent. Leg formula 1243, ALE&gt; PLE&gt; PME&gt; AME. AER, PER recurved, eyes on brown-coloured mounds, but not touching. Palps as in 
<figureCitation box="[615,709,1027,1051]" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="7.[160,225,1202,1225]" captionTargetBox="[177,1151,142,1171]" captionTargetId="figure-95@7.[163,1152,142,1171]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figure 3. Epidius coloratus sp. nov. RMNH 15921. (a) Male palp, ventral view. (b) Same, retrolateral view. Scale bars = 0.2 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5184391" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5184391/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="474">Figure 3</figureCitation>
(a, b), femur and tibia characteristically elongated, femur as long as tibia, furnished with 6 thick spines and MTr. RTA present, ovoid, curved. Bulbus ovoid. C ovate, curved tip surrounds E. MA present in between C and tegulum. Embolus broad based, filiform (
<figureCitation box="[669,761,1131,1155]" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="7.[160,225,1202,1225]" captionTargetBox="[177,1151,142,1171]" captionTargetId="figure-95@7.[163,1152,142,1171]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figure 3. Epidius coloratus sp. nov. RMNH 15921. (a) Male palp, ventral view. (b) Same, retrolateral view. Scale bars = 0.2 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5184391" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5184391/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="474">Figure 3</figureCitation>
(a, b)).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[160,383,1199,1224]" box="[160,383,1199,1224]" pageId="6" pageNumber="474">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,252,1199,1224]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="474">Female.</emphasis>
Unknown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
